channel.title: Run.Bat doesnt work!
channel.description:
I have Jdk 13 update and my current run.bat:
@echo off title DeltaScape "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin\java.exe" -cp .;./bin; -Xmx800M server pause
.. The error I get is:
Cannot find the path specified
Someone help?
